content:
Actionable Relationship Center (ARC) lets you view your insurance customers' relationships in an easy-to-navigate graph. ARC helps you understand relationships among people and businesses by presenting them in interactive components.

Use Default Templates in the Actionable Relationship Center for Insurance
Use preconfigured ARC graph templates to build relationship graphs for Insurance.

You can improve! Yes
title: Actionable Relationship Center (ARC) in Salesforce Insurance
